      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for all your weekend adventures? I\u2019m parting ways with this beauty, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and has been well-loved and taken care of. It's the perfect match for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I do! \u2728",
      "price": 29500.0,
