    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E36 M3 is a purist\u2019s driving machine, featuring the S50 inline-six power plant with single-VANOS variable valve timing for a broad, accessible torque curve. The longitudinal drivetrain is mated to a crisp ZF 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory-equipped 3.15 limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and exit speeds. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent refresh of the rear trailing arm bushings and front control arm bushings to preserve the legendary steering feedback and turn-in precision. The cooling system has been reinforced with an aluminum radiator to mitigate common heat-cycle fatigue. While the exterior shows minor evidence of road use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all cylinders and the integrity of the subframe mounting points\u2014are robust, making this an ideal candidate for the spirited driver who prioritizes analog performance and engineering longevity.",
